quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,67,"Si he…ìii on -ko onon yo sirkoo…ìe- jarrabuyee e huunde a√±√±iinde ka maayo haa tawa on hulii halkaaree, wirnoto ka miijo mon kon ko laatino …óon hi…óon rewa ko woori Alla, on jantotaako si wanah Alla …óa…ì…ìiron Mo faabo, tuma nde O faabii on O hisini on immorde e ko huluno…óon kon, wontu…óon ka njorndi …óurno…óon e ngootimbaaku Makko e noddugol Mo Kanko tun, rutto…óon e sanamuuji mon, ne…ó…óanke on laatike ko o heewu…óo yeddugol neemaaji Alla …óin."
  17,68,"Kaa on hooli -ko onon yo sirkoo…ìe- tuma Alla danndi on ka njorndi O wa…óataa haa ndi yulina on=ndi yirba e mon? Kaa on hooli O jippintaa e mon kaa∆¥e immorde ka kammu …óe to…ìa e mon wano O wa…óirinon e yim…ìe Luutu, refti on he…ìataa deeno mo no reena on, wanaa ballo mo no ha…óana on halkeede."
  17,69,"Kaa on hooli Alla artirtaa on ka maayo laawol goo, refti O nula e mon henndu sattundu, O yoola on sabu yeddugol mon neemaaji Alla …óin, tuma nde O danndunoo on ka aranun, refti he…ìantaake on …óa…ì…ìoowo mo no …óa…ì…ìira Men yettanagol on ko Men wa…ói on kon."
  17,70,"Gom…óii Men teddinirii ge…óal…ìe Aadama …ìen hakkille e ko Maalaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen sujjani kon baaba ma…ì…ìa e ko wonaa …óun kadi, Men eltani …ìe daabeeji e mba…ó…óateeji ko ronndoo …ìe ka njorndi e laa…óe ko ronndoo …ìe ka maayo, Men arsiki …ìe laa…ìu…ói ka √±aameteeji e ka njaram e ka desal e tanaa mun. Men …ìurni …ìe e dow ko …óuu…ói immorde e tageefooji Amen …ìural mawngal, no fawii…ìe jarnugol neema mo Alla neeminiri …ìe on."
  17,71,"Ja≈ãto -an Nulaa…óo- √±ennde Men noddirta kala fedde yeesoojo mayre, on mo nde laatinoo hinde √±intina ka aduna, kala jonnitiraa…óo deftere golle mun ka √±aamo makko …ìen …óon …ìe janngay deftere ma…ì…ìe nden hi…ìe weltii, …ìe ustantaake huunde e njoddi ma…ì…ìe ndin, hay si no fan…óiri wa kun gaara hun wonu kun e po…ó…óere tamoro."
  17,72,"Kala on laatii…óo e …óam ngurndan aduna ko o wumu…óo gii…óe …ìernde gaayi jabugol goonga e yankinanagol goonga, haray kanko ko √±alde darngal o …ìurata wumude, o feewirtaa laawol Aljanna ngol, ko ton kadi o …ìurata majjude gaayi e laawol peewal, njoddi ndin ko e noone golle …óen."
  17,73,"Gom…óii sirkoo…ìe …ìen do'iino firlide ma -an Nulaa…óo- e kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa immorde e Alqur'aana; fii yo a fefindo e Amen ko wonaa …óun, ko hawrondirta kon e belee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, si a wa…óuno ko …ìe faalaa kon e …óun …ìe su…ìutonoma gi…óo."
  17,74,"Si tawiino Men neeminiraali ma tabintingol ma e hoore goonga kan, gom…óii hari a …ìadike oo√±aade e ma…ì…ìe yoga e oo√±agol, ja…ìanaa …ìe ko …ìe fewjanmaa kon, sabu tii…óugol hodo ma…ì…ìe e sa…ótugol janfaaji ma…ì…ìe wonndude e fantude rer…óugol maa e gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe, kono Men reenumaa e oo√±agol faade e ma…ì…ìe."
  17,75,"Si a oo√±ino e ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe fewjanaymaa kon Men henneteno lepte sowaa…óe ka ngurndan aduna e ka laahara, refti a he…ìataa ballo mo no walle e hoore Amen, o ittane lepte …óen."